        "subject": "LU-18356 tests: fix skipping symbolic version code",
        "message": "LU-18356 tests: fix skipping symbolic version code\n\nAllow the except/*.ex file to exclude a subtest based on the symbolic\nversion code (e.g. \"CLIENT_VERSION\", rather than the numeric version.\nThe symbolic version needs to be evaluated in order to work correctly.\n\nTest-Parameters: trivial\nFixes: c4c3a7350b (\"LU-18356 tests: allow server to specify except list\")\nSigned-off-by: Andreas Dilger <adilger@whamcloud.com>\nChange-Id: Id27bd86ce295b2ad3fda041baa776a72442540e5\nReviewed-on: https://review.whamcloud.com/c/fs/lustre-release/+/60218\nReviewed-by: Frederick Dilger <fdilger@whamcloud.com>\nTested-by: Maloo <maloo@whamcloud.com>\nTested-by: jenkins <devops@whamcloud.com>\n"
      },
